      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted 996.2 Carrera 2, powered by the 3.6L M96 flat-six engine featuring VarioCam Plus for an optimized torque curve. This chassis has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh rear main seal. The G96 6-speed manual transaxle shifts with mechanical precision, while the suspension retains its factory-spec damping characteristics, providing the signature rear-engine pendulum effect and communicative hydraulic steering feedback. The cooling system has been upgraded with a low-temperature thermostat to manage thermal loads effectively. While the exterior displays honest patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the powertrain and drivetrain remain high-performing and track-capable. Equipped with four-piston monobloc calipers and cross-drilled rotors for consistent thermal dissipation during spirited driving.",
      "price": 32800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
