    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a stunning 2017 Porsche 718 Cayman finished in Agate Grey Metallic. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained with a focus on mechanical longevity and aesthetic preservation. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scratch on the rear bumper reflect its history as an enjoyed driver\u2019s car. Inside, the cabin is remarkably crisp; the black leather seats remain firm and supportive, showing only very light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every interior feature, from the responsive PCM infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this Porsche is turn-key and ready for the road. It comes with a comprehensive service history, including a major service completed just 3,000 miles ago which saw the replacement of spark plugs, filters, and a brake fluid flush. The staggered wheels are free of curb rash and are wrapped in high-performance tires with significant tread remaining. This is an excellent opportunity to own a well-documented, reliable sports car that perfectly balances track-bred performance with daily comfort.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
